aa(lp30
VSo, a little bit of perspective \u2014
p31
aVabout 10,000 years of perspective.
p32
aVThis is a trephinated skull.
p33
aVAnd trephination is simply just cutting a hole in the skull.
p34
aVAnd many, many hundreds of skulls like this
p35
aVhave been found in archaeological sites
p36
aVall over the world,
p37
aVdating back five to 10 thousand years.
p38
aVFive to 10 thousand years! Now imagine this.
