aa(lp49
VNow we've got the dawn of interventional surgery here.
p50
aVWhat is astonishing about this is,
p51
aVeven though we don't know really how much of this
p52
aVwas intended to be religious,
p53
aVor how much of it was intended to be therapeutic,
p54
aVwhat we can tell is that these patients lived!
