aa(lp146
VThe era of the "big surgeon, big incision" had arrived,
p147
aVbut at quite a cost,
p148
aVbecause they are saving lives,
p149
aVbut not necessarily quality of life,
p150
aVbecause healthy people don't usually need surgery,
p151
aVand unhealthy people have a very hard time recovering from a cut like that.
